## What's Changed
* [MSHADE-369] update commons-lang by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/49
* [MSHADE-370] update mockito by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/50
* Bump asmVersion from 8.0 to 8.0.1 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/57
* MSHADE-373: adds a property to skip manifest transformer application when transforming a source file. by @raphw in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/59
* [MSHADE-378] Shade plugin changes the compression level of nested jar… by @jenrryyou in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/73
* Bump guava from 28.2-android to 30.0-android by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/75
* remove unused private method by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/79
* remove deprecated method by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/78
* Bump asmVersion from 9.0 to 9.1 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/84
* Bump junit from 4.13 to 4.13.2 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/86
* [MSHADE-252] - Make source shading respect package/class name excludes by @kriegaex in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/88
* Bump slf4j-api from 1.7.30 to 1.7.31 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/101
* [MSHADE-382] - Add property to skip execution by @aalmiray in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/90
* Bump slf4j-simple from 1.7.30 to 1.7.31 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/102
* Bump asmVersion from 9.1 to 9.2 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/106
* Bump jdependency from 2.6.0 to 2.7.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/99
* run gh action with more jdk by @olamy in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/111
* Bump slf4j.version from 1.7.31 to 1.7.32 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/113
* [MSHADE-396] Improve SourceContent Shading by @kriegaex in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/105
* [MSHADE-405] - ShowOverlapping Uses http instead of https by @khmarbaise in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/118
* Bump sisu.version from 0.3.4 to 0.3.5 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/117
* [MSHADE-412] avoid possible NPE since rawString was added in SimpleRelocator by @rmannibucau in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/123
* Bump hamcrest-core from 1.3 to 2.2 by @dependabot in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/96

## New Contributors
* @raphw made their first contribution in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/59
* @jenrryyou made their first contribution in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/73
* @kriegaex made their first contribution in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/88
* @aalmiray made their first contribution in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/90
* @khmarbaise made their first contribution in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/118

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/compare/maven-shade-plugin-3.2.4...maven-shade-plugin-3.3.0

## What's Changed
* deps: update JUnit to 4.13 by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/41
* [MSHADE-351] make constructors public by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/45
* [MSHADE-359] update guava by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/42
* use try with resources to close streams and fix warnings by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/43
* [MSHADE-360] avoid PrintWriter by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/44
* [MSHADE-361] specify UTF-8 encoding per Java spec by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/46
* [MSHADE-364] drop duplicates handled by a transformer by @rmannibucau in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/48
* MSHADE-363 add ReproducibleResourceTransformer to restore compatibility by @hboutemy in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/47

## New Contributors
* @hboutemy made their first contribution in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/47

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/compare/maven-shade-plugin-3.2.3...maven-shade-plugin-3.2.4

## What's Changed
* [MSHADE-291] - Fixes bug in ServicesResourceTransformer by @fabcipriano in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/9
* [MSHADE-318] - Include transitive dependencies by @mkarg in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/20
* [MSHADE-306] log all duplicates to not silently swallow a duplicate and an implicit selection by @rmannibucau in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/10
* [MSHADE-327] improved integration test coverage for relocation and minification by @tcurdt in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/27
* upgrade to asm 7.2 by @sullis in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/29
* Update CONTRIBUTING hyperlinks by @ItsFlare in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/36
* fix typo by @elharo in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/37

## New Contributors

* Jdk11 support by @olamy in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/5
* [MSHADE-303] Suppress module-info.class warning if the file if filtered by @danilcha in https://github.com/apache/maven-shade-plugin/pull/8
